## Write a program to convert minutes to seconds

1 minute = 60 seconds

```
Input  : 5
Output : 300
```

---

<CodeBlock slug="convert-minutes-to-seconds" >

```c
#include <stdio.h>

int main(){
    int n;
    scanf("%d",&n);
    printf("%d\n",n*60);
    return 0;
}

//Contributed by Raghav Garg
